We're on GitHub.

00:19:15.000 --> 00:19:28.000
We've got a brand-new GitHub organization, MVRX Web, where you will find the source code as well as dozens of middleware and plugins, if you like, for MVRX.

00:19:28.000 --> 00:19:35.000
We've got a nice website that's been redone recently by Kennedy at mvrx.dev.

00:19:35.000 --> 00:19:40.000
And you've got these nice slides also done by Kennedy on GitHub.

00:19:40.000 --> 00:19:44.000
It's on CRAN, so you just have to go install.packages.mvrx.

00:19:44.000 --> 00:19:46.000
We hope you give it a spin.

